OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day with some
OL,6,Fpatchy, mainly light rain. There will
OL,7,Fbe some drier and perhaps brighter
OL,8,Fspells too, especially later in the
OL,9,Fwest. Quite mild with mainly light
OL,10,Fsouth or southwest winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPatchy rain clearing the east
OL,13,Fthis evening then drier for a time.
OL,14,FCloud thickening again overnight with
OL,15,Fsome rain or drizzle returning
OL,16,Fovernight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FCloudy with occasional rain
OL,19,Fin the morning then brightening up
OL,20,Fwith a few showers. Heavier rain in
OL,21,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
